<body style="background-color: #120E1B;">

    <!-- ruleVR -->
    <div class="ruleVR">
        <div class="ruleVRWrapper">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="titleContent">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("GameInformation","CreatorProject")'">
                        <
                    </button>
                    <div class="title">
                        Rating rules for audio recording
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- ruleVRLoading -->
                <div class="ruleVRLoading">
                    <div class="ruleVRContainer">
                        <div class="addForm">
                            <p class="desc">
                                Epal.gg is dedicated to creating a social gaming platform where users can
                                safely and creatively express themselves. To reach this goal, please observe our
                                <a href="https://policies.epal.gg/multimedia-policy.html?theme=dark">
                                    Multimedia
                                    Policy
                                </a> when uploading images to your game application. You can read the full
                                policy here Multimedia Policy. These policies apply to all genders.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- criterias -->
                <div class="criterias">
                    <h6>Rating criterias :</h6>
                    <p>1. The quality of the audio track, and its background noise;</p>
                    <p>2. Whether you have introduced yourself;</p>
                    <p>3. Whether you have talked about your in-game skills and/or preferences;</p>
                    <p>
                        4. Excellent is 80 and above, Good is 60 to 79, Moderate is 40 to 59, and Poor is 39 and below;
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        5. This rating for your voice line is a review system to improve the overall quality of your
                        store page, and hence removal of potential issues.
                    </p>
                    <p>6. Voice recording must be in English.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- example -->
                <div class="example">
                    <h6>Example :</h6>
                </div>

                <!-- tips -->
                <div class="tips">
                    <h6>Tips :</h6>
                    <p>
                        1. Record your line in a quiet environment with a decent quality microphone, and try to keep your
                        volume consistent;
                    </p>
                    <p>2. Don’t speak too fast nor too slow, make yourself easy to understand;</p>
                    <p>3. It should include self-introduction;</p>
                    <p>
                        4. It should include your experience, skill and preference in the game, such as “Gold Jungle
                        main”;
                    </p>
                    <p>5. Humour is a great selling point, so tell some jokes if you have any.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

